ctrum to deliver terrestrial wireless service but that waiver is on hold pending resolution of interference issues with gps which uses an adjacent spectrum band montagners resume includes postings at banc of america securities morgan stanley and svp corporate development and mergers and acquisitions for sprint nextel tagsyou may also like next article anne roberts nelson year cbs veteran diesview the discussion thread inside the current issue as the bundle unravels relationships shift too slinging away from the pack editorial quality over quantity with new initiative tegna stations manage to verify then trust editorial some help for lptv the five spot jon litner archive more sign up for our newsletters subscribe now pr wiresonnet technologies at ibcbluebell opticom at ibcphabrix at ibcosprey video at ibcsumma schools broadcast students atmatrix solutions continues growth with more from the wire schmoozephoto galleries of celebrities and industry leaders jul   jul   jun   jun   jun   may   may   headlines from our affiliates liberatore upped at outdoor sportsman groupdescendants  draws  million viewers in live   datalgbt tech vows to fight trump transgender ban etrs  is up and running weekly tech reminders fm translators national eas test and moreinovonics announces s retirement eas test reporting system now opentivo highlights voice search for personalized content discovery platformnetwork management for ip and storage detroit and the ghosts of historythe innovative underwater production of chasing coralprimetime presidency producing the reagan show endurance international group announces executive appointments nasdaqeigi english français register sign in endurance international group announces executive appointments marc montagner chief financial officer appointed interim chief operating officer allen m chaves jr as chief technology officer may    et  source endurance international group photorelease marc montagner cfo  interim coo marc montagner cfo  interim coo endurance international group allen chaves jr cto allen chaves jr cto endurance international group burlington mass may   globe newswire  endurance international group holdings inc nasdaqeigi a leading provider of cloud based platform solutions today announced that marc montagner has been appointed interim chief operating officer in addition to his current position as chief financial officer effective immediately mr montagner has served as endurance’s cfo since september  and will continue to report to hari ravichandran the company’s founder and chief executive officer until the ceo transition plan is completed as previously announced endurance is actively conducting a search to identify mr ravichandran’s successor mr montagner has nearly  years of extensive experience across relevant industries having previously served as cfo at lightsquared inc as well as executive vice president of strategy development and distribution at the satellite communications company he also served as managing partner of dupont circle partners llc as well as managing director and cohead of the global telecom media and technology merger and acquisition group at banc of america securities until  he was senior vice president corporate development and ma with the sprint nextel corporation prior to  mr montagner was a managing director in the media and telecom group at morgan stanley “marc has served endurance well during his tenure and we welcome his strong operating experience” said hari ravichandran “we expect that this expanded role will ensure consistency within the organization as the company evolves and we transition leadership” endurance also announced the appointment of allen m chaves jr as the company’s new chief technology officer chaves brings  years of technology strategy and software architecture experience with him to endurance where he will spearhead the vision and strategic direction for all of the company’s software offerings he will directly lead the software engineering teams for endurance and will work closely with executive management to implement platforms that support the business strategy ensuring endurance’s products technology platforms and architectures evolve to support emerging customer and market opportunities “we’re pleased to have allen join our team to help improve the technology capabilities of our software offerings across our key brands” said hari ravichandran “as we continue to make operational improvements across the company we’re committed to investing in the right talent to help us become better positioned in the marketplace i’m confident that with allen’s leadership and platform architecture expertise we’re well on our way to meeting our business goals” chaves has led the technology architecture teams at several notable technology organizations he joins endurance after serving most recently as chief software architect for ultimate software where he led the technology strategy and architecture for ultimate’s saas products shared services big data and cloud previously chaves served as chief architect and director of engineering for the quickbooks online platform at intuit in this role chaves was responsible for all aspects of the technology and architecture of an m business unit and led a team of senior engineering leaders and architects he also held the position of principal software architect for sage where he led the creation of sage’s saas hrms product chaves holds a bachelor of science degree in computer science from the universidade federal de minas gerais in brazil forwardlooking statements this press release includes certain “forwardlooking statements” within the meaning of the private securities litigation reform act of  section a of the securities act of  as amended and section e of the securities exchange act of  as amended including statements concerning our beliefs and expectations about our future executive leadership organizational structure and contributions of mr montagner and mr chaves these forwar